<p>&amp; the troops who were here before us were responsible for it.   The name of this Camp is Erie" they are Canadian places &amp; are named after Canadian towns &amp; lakes some of them are these.<br/>Ontario, Erie, Michigan, Princess Patricia's Quebec &amp; etc.</p>
